						<summary>

						<p>This is an incomplete inscription of Parāntaka I (Madiraikoṇḍa Parakēsarivarman) recording some gift made for burning a lamp in the temple by Śerupadaṉ Subrahmaṇyaṉ a resident of Kuḻittaṇḍalai in Kuṟumbūr-nāḍu. This place is evidently the same as Kuḷittalai near Karur in the Tiruchirappalli district.</p>						

						</summary>
